    <em>Thank you for sharing the blurb below.</em>
    <p>The Illinois Network of Charter Schools (INCS) will host its <a href="www.incschools.org/tjf">12th annual Teacher Job Fair</a> on Saturday, March 18, 2017 at ASPIRA Business & Finance Campus. Representatives from the state’s charter schools will be on hand to recruit hundreds of teachers, social workers, counselors, nurses, and other administrators - such as marketing managers, college coaches, and finance operators.  You can learn more about the FREE fair and upload your resume to the year-round resume bank <a href="www.teacherjobfair.org">here</a>.</p>
    <p>Some of the great features of the job fair include:</p>
    <ul>
