      <li>Per charter law, students and alumni of all academic backgrounds are welcome to apply</li>
    </ul>
    <p>For more information, contact Charter Support Manager, Stephanie Arias, at <a href="mailto:sarias@incschools.org" target="_top">sarias@incschools.org</a>.</p>
